The paper is about a large-scale video corpus and event ontology, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) model for event classification, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of linear SVM for binary classification, which is relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
